_sText:
This is the final version of gg_nasty_neighbours, I have improved a few things from the beta such as:
Spawn points moved around to elliminate seeing the enemy at spawn/spawn killing
Walls on bridges now changed to small fences/railings
Chimneys added on roof
Lighting adjusted inside the houses
A few props added
Optimized fps
and a few other details

cheers, Elliot and the GG Nuts studio!
